@Update to imlib2-1.3.0. Initial diffs from 'bsdmaniak at daemon-tips dot org'
and brad@@.

This contains security fixes from the imlib2 cvs repository for CVE-2006-4806,
CVE-2006-4807, CVE-2006-4808 and CVE-2006-4809.

ok brad@@, steven@@
